subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Jamie McMurray would probably not have ended his 166-race winless streak Saturday night without the help of his Roush Fenway Racing teammates Matt Kenseth and Carl Edwards.
